---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'March 2025';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for chrisjbell.com and the Kate AI job coaching agent."
>
  <div class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <!-- Page header -->
    <header class="mb-12 border-b border-border pb-10">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium text-ink-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-ink tracking-display">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-3">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="prose max-w-2xl">
      <p>
        This privacy policy applies to chrisjbell.com and any associated products,
        including the Kate AI job coaching agent ("Kate", "the Service"). Please read this
        policy carefully to understand how information is collected, used, and protected.
      </p>

      <h2>Information Collected</h2>

      <h3>Information you provide directly</h3>
      <p>
        When you use Kate or contact me through this site, you may provide information
        including your name, email address, and details about your job search (such as
        your resume, target roles, and interview experiences). This information is used
        solely to provide the coaching service.
      </p>

      <h3>Conversation data</h3>
      <p>
        Kate is built on Anthropic's Claude. Conversations you have with Kate may be
        processed by Anthropic in accordance with their privacy policy and terms of
        service. I do not store full conversation transcripts independently, though
        session context is maintained during active conversations.
      </p>

      <h3>Usage information</h3>
      <p>
        This site may collect standard usage information such as browser type, referring
        pages, and pages visited. This data is used only in aggregate to understand how
        the site is being used and is not linked to individual identities.
      </p>

      <h2>How Information Is Used</h2>
      <p>
        Information you provide is used to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deliver and improve the Kate coaching service</li>
        <li>Respond to questions or requests you send directly</li>
        <li>Understand aggregate usage patterns to improve the site</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Your information is not sold, rented, or shared with third parties for marketing
        purposes.
      </p>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Personal information is retained only as long as necessary to provide the service
        or respond to your request. You may request deletion of your data at any time by
        contacting me directly.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Kate is built on Anthropic's Claude API. By using Kate, you acknowledge that your
        conversation inputs are processed by Anthropic. Please review{' '}
        <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Anthropic's Privacy Policy
        </a>{' '}
        to understand how they handle data.
      </p>

      <h2>Security</h2>
      <p>
        I take reasonable precautions to protect information from unauthorized access or
        disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely
        secure, and I cannot guarantee absolute security.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of any
        personal information I hold about you. To exercise these rights, contact me using
        the information below.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        This policy may be updated from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page
        with a revised "last updated" date. Continued use of the site or services after
        changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about this privacy policy or to make a data request, please contact:
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Chris Bell</strong><br />
        <a href="mailto:privacy@chrisjbell.com">privacy@chrisjbell.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="py-8"></div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
